      "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> You drink an ignition vial, then blow a cloud of deadly energy from your mouth. Creatures in a @Template[cone|distance:15] take @Damage[(1+ceil(@actor.level / 2))d4[fire]|options:area-damage] damage with a @Check[reflex|against:slayer|basic|options:area-effect] save against your class DC. The damage increases by 1d4 at 3rd level and every 2 levels thereafter.</p><p><strong>Reinforced</strong> Ignition Vial deals one of the trophy's non-physical damage types, if any, instead of fire, and has the matching trait instead of fire.</p>",
